:<font size="15">עטה</font></div>

===Pronunciation===
עטה / ‛âṭâh / aw-taw'

===Etymology===
A primitive root; 

===Verb===
'''עטה'''

# To wrap, that is, cover, veil, clothe or roll: - array, self, be clad, (put a) cover (-ing, self), fill, put on, X surely, turn aside.

